                        Thursday, July 16, 1953</hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d79fn1">No memorandum of discussion of this meeting has been
                        found. Copies of the minutes of those <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss>
                        meetings held during the Presidency of <persName
                            corresp="#p_EISENHOWERGADD1">Dwight D. Eisenhower</persName> are filed
                        in the <persName corresp="#p_EISENHOWERGADD1">Eisenhower</persName> Library,
                            <persName corresp="#p_EISENHOWERGADD1">Eisenhower</persName> papers,
                            <persName>Whitman</persName> file. They consist of a list of those
                        present along with a record of decisions reached and therefore are much less
                        complete in their coverage than the memoranda of discussion. Although
                        frequent allusion is made in the memoranda of discussion to documents and
                        papers filed with the minutes of a given <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss>
                        meeting, such documents have generally not been found with the
                        minutes.</note>
                </head>
